[SN]TITLE[SN]
Tom Huddlestone: Hull City midfielder signs new contract

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Hull City midfielder Tom Huddlestone has signed a new two-year contract with the newly-promoted Premier League club.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Huddlestone has made 123 appearances for Hull since signing from Tottenham for a fee of about Â£5m in August 2013.
The 29-year-old Derby academy-graduate played in 47 games last term to help the Tigers earn promotion through the Championship play-offs.
"It's been a rollercoaster three years, but I've enjoyed my time here and I'm settled," he told BBC Radio Humberside.
